items.text:
## **CASTING CALL – “Tale of Two” (Short Film)**

**Logline:**
*“Tale of Two”* is a portrait short film about women’s strength, focusing on our shared experiences rather than our differences. Through small, intimate scenes, we witness key moments in the lives of two women as they navigate hardship, love, and resilience in parallel journeys.

**Production Details:**
* **Location:** Downtown Vancouver
* **Shoot Dates:** 1-3 days – end of January
* **Format:** MOS (no sync sound) – performances will rely heavily on expressive, facial acting
* **Union Status:** Non-Union / Volunteer Passion Project
* **Compensation:** Volunteer basis with **great meals, greater company, and IMDb credit**.
Select roles (requiring multiple full days) will receive a **small honorarium**.

**To Submit:**
Please send your **headshot and CV/demo reel**, which **role** you’re applying for and a **self-tape** with the attached actions **taleoftwofilm@gmail.com**.
Include a **slate** with your **name, age, height,** and any **unavailable dates**.
**Submission Deadline:** *November 25th at midnight.*

Casting Call!

*Starchild* is a sci-fi drama that follows the story of two scientists, Vanessa and Tanner as they take separate paths to deal with their grief. Vanessa through faith, and Tanner through science. It's not until they discover the origins of life itself, that they reconcile to start a family of their own. 

The film is heartfelt, honest, and powerful.

Please send resume, headshot, and (if applicable) demo reel to starchildcasting@gmail.com

**ISO: 15-FT Production Truck Driver (PA)  - Indie Film**

We are seeking a reliable Driver(PA) for our micro-budget indie film.

**Non-Union**

**Location:** Los Angeles Area
**Position:** 15ft Production Truck Driver
**Rate:** $18.19/hour

**Responsibilities:**
* Pick up production truck and deliver to set location
* Return to set after wrap to pick up truck and transport to next location
* Ensure safe and timely transport of production vehicle
* Loading & unloading truck with other assistance

**Work Dates:**
* Thursday, December 4, 2025 (pick up day)
* Friday, December 5, 2025
* Saturday, December 6, 2025
* Sunday, December 7, 2025
* Monday, December 8, 2025
* Tuesday, December 9, 2025
* Friday, December 12, 2025 (potentially - not definite)
* Saturday, December 13, 2025
* Sunday, December 14, 2025
* Monday, December 15, 2025
* Tuesday, December 16, 2025
* Wednesday, December 17, 2025
* Thursday, December 18, 2025 (return day)

**Hours:** These will not be full shooting days. Hours may range from 4 to 6 hours per day as needed for vehicle transport.

**Requirements:**
* Valid driver's license
* Clean driving record
* Experience driving larger vehicles/trucks preferred
* Punctual and dependable

If interested, please submit your resume, a message regarding your interest/experience, and 3 references to info@saltpicturesco.com with your availability and any questions about the position.

sharedPost.text:
I am Thomas Goersch from Stuttgart Germany. 
Actor and Filmdirector. 
I am making Independent Movies and some kind of Art House Underground Movies. I present my movies on International Film festivals and was lucky to receive some awards. 
But the work is not about awards and money, its about making movies for the people to think about.
My next movie is a modern love story:
An elderly man is meeting another younger, very attractive man in the Internet.  But they are from different Continents. They start a long distance relastionship ship. which is full of passion and desire. 
One day the younger man starts to ask for money, cause he is a Student and no more able to pay his bills. 
The older man is full of distrust.
Is he only there  to pay his lovers bills or is there love between them ?
A story with two endings.
One with true love and one with betrayl.

I am looking for the young attraktive Lover.
Men  25 to 42 years old,  good looking  who is able to film his parts on his own by smartshone
I am always open and honest. You can earn no money on this. but maybe there is a good film in the end promoting for you.
I guess its not necessary that an educated actor is playing this part. so feel free to get in touch

Thats me 
www.imdb.com/name/nm1591928

Get in touch under Thomas.Goersch@vodafonemail.de 

please ask for details.

items.text:
Do serialu „Gliniarze” realizowane w Warszawie poszukuję aktorki roli:

Sekretarka (41) – pracuje w firmie-krzaku należącej do oszusta. Nerwowa, przerażona, gdy dowiaduje się kto jest jej szefem. Ma problem alkoholowy. 

Data: 26. i 27.11

Stawka: 700 zł netto za całość

 

Chętne Panie zapraszam do wysyłania zgłoszeń na adres: casting.outset@interia.pl

W tytule maila proszę o wpisanie nazwy postaci.

W treści maila proszę o zawarcie następujących informacji:

1. Wiek/wzrost/waga

2. Nr tel. Do kontaktu

3. Krótki opis doświadczenia

4. Linki do sowich materiałów video – demo/wizytówka/scenki castingowe

5. Aktualne zdjęcie

Nie zwracamy kosztów dojazdu/noclegu

Szukam na plan programu rozrywkowego osób które będą się świetnie bawiły, uśmiechały, robiły zdjęcia itp.

Zdjecia w centrum w godzinach 8-12:30 maksymalnie.

Czekam na wasze zgłoszenia:)

Marta 😙

Du kommst aus Berlin und Umgebung? Wir suchen dich!

​

Wir suchen Schauspieler:innen, Darsteller:innen, Kompars:innen, Protagonist:innen und Künstler:innen aus Berlin und Umgebung für Filme, Serien, Werbung und vieles mehr.

​

Über unsere interne Kartei vermitteln wir regelmäßig Jobs und Castings in der Schauspiel- und Medienbranche – direkt und unkompliziert.

​

👉 Der Eintrag ist kostenlos – kommentiere einfach mit “BERLIN” und erhalte den Link zur Anmeldung!

Oder kennst du jemanden, der aus der Nähe von Berlin. kommt? Dann markiere ihn!

​

Wir freuen uns auf dich ❤️

Dein Castfinder-Team

Hi, ich bin Rony – Schauspieler und Online Coach.
Ich unterstütze bei Castings, Selftapes und arbeite gemeinsam mit euch an Szenen.

Ich arbeite mit Anfänger*innen, Schauspieler*innen am Beginn ihrer Karriere und auch mit erfahrenen Profis, die ihre Arbeit vertiefen möchten.

Schreibt mir gern für weitere Infos oder um eine Session zu vereinbaren.
Mehr über mich findet ihr hier: [Mein IMDb-Profil](https://www.imdb.com/de/name/nm4236291/)

Liebe Grüße
Rony

early December Shoot (date tbd)

To play the villain in an Intense Crime Drama short.

£300 for 1-Day-Shoot plus half a day of rehearsals.

Please send in a cover letter with your resume with headshot and your showreel to Davina Brown at k2filmworks@gmail.com Please do not respond in the comments or via DM.

items.text:
Hello! I am a casting director in London looking for a man in his 40s to play a Dealer in a music video shooting on 24th November. 

We are specifically looking for someone who can do card tricks to be the card dealer. A Doug Jones looking character but not necessarily. Could this be you? 

The shoot is set in a poker bar and the plot of the music video is a heist. The pay rate for the Dealer is £200 for the day. 

If you are interested - please email me ASAP with -recent headshot -full name -instagram handle -phone number -email

—— > lily.lepage@free.fr

topComments.text: How about doug Jones with long hair, knuckle tattoos and grills?

items.text:
Hi! 

I’m currently casting a well paid shoot for an alcohol brand

As it’s advertising for alcohol all cast legally need to be at least 25 (production will ask for id to prove this if shortlisted by client) however the concept for the project is quite youthful so max age should be 30. 

Casting Brief: 

Looking for European girls with coloured hair (think red, blue, pink, green, berry, purple) or happy to have their hair coloured for the shoot. 

Looking for European boys with facial hair (a moustache and/or beard - bonus if you have an interesting hair cut too) 

This is a London shoot so looking for London based people only. 

**Shoot Dates: **Thursday 27th + Friday 28th November

Talent to attend both shoot days in London on Location

Based on a 10 hour shoot day including an additional hour for lunch

**Fitting Date:** Monday 24th November, 1-2 hours in London (between 9am and 6pm)

**Talent Age: **All Talent to be over 25 and passport or ID needs to be provided at the time of shortlist to confirm this 

**Talent Rates:**

Talent Day Rates - £600 per person per day

Talent Usage* £5,000 per model

*Usage not guaranteed however all talent are shot in groups so this is very likely to be confirmed

**Talent Wardrobe:**

Talent will be required to bring a couple of outfits to the shoot which will be briefed by the wardrobe stylist

and either brought to the fitting or photographed before the shoot.

£50 per person (total not per day)

To submit please fill in this form : 

[https://airtable.com/apprDbNv50EdHz0RT/pagpszb0AEzQg5XCi/form](https://airtable.com/apprDbNv50EdHz0RT/pagpszb0AEzQg5XCi/form)

And, please upload your self tape here: [https://www.dropbox.com/request/s2OXkOWhOSaif9oUoaCR](https://www.dropbox.com/request/s2OXkOWhOSaif9oUoaCR)

The deadline is 10AM, Monday 17th November. 

No requests, no PM’s 

Thank you! 

www.unit-c.co

items.text:
Cześć 😋

SOS! Sytuacja jest taka, że planuję zdawać na aktorstwo i muszę przygotować kilka rzeczy: prozę, wiersze, piosenkę i taniec — wszystko po polsku (czyli cały twórczy egzamin). Dlatego muszę zabrać się za to już teraz i Wasza pomoc byłaby dla mnie naprawdę bardzo ważna!

Chciałam zapytać:
– gdzie mogę znaleźć informacje o castingach czyli jak oni się odbywają ?
– gdzie można uczyć się aktorstwa bez oficjalnych kursów?
- czy mogę chodzić na wasze korepetycje?
– czy macie może znajomych na uczelniach  teatralnych lub filmowych, którzy wiedzą, jak wygląda rekrutacja i sam proces przyjęć?
– albo może macie jakieś rady dotyczące gry aktorskiej albo inne informacje, którymi moglibyście się podzielić?

Będę ogromnie wdzięczna za każdą pomoc 💕

items.text:
**🎬 CASTING CALL – Background Actors Needed! 🎬**

We’re looking for **background actors** for our upcoming **independent feature film *****Express Entry*** shooting in **Surrey, BC**.

📅 **Dates & Requirements:**
* **Nov 29:** 6 background actors needed
* **Nov 30:** 4 background actors needed
* **Time:** Approx. 4 hours each day
* **Location:** Surrey, BC
* **Open to all genders and ethnicities**
* These are **different scenes on both days**, so we’re looking for **different people each day** (no repeats).

🎥 **About the Project:**
This is a **volunteer position** – perfect for anyone who wants to **gain experience on a film set**, be part of a **fun shoot**, and **network with passionate filmmakers**.

🍪 **Perks:**
* Crafty (snacks & refreshments) provided
* **IMDb credit**
* A great opportunity to see how an indie film set works!

If interested, please email your **name, photo, and availability** to **expressentryfilm@gmail.com** with the subject line **“Background Actor – Express Entry.”**

Come join the team and be part of something special! 🎥✨

items.text:
My name is Jerry Valentino Wright — published author of 11 books and creator of multiple cinematic universes that are READY to be adapted to film.

I’m seeking one serious, visionary producer or small production company who sees potential where others see limits — someone who wants to help bring a powerful, original franchise to life.

I have several finished books that are visually explosive, emotionally gripping, and built for the screen, including:

🎬 The Eternal War: Light vs Darkness —
A supernatural action-drama with apocalyptic tension, angelic warfare, moral conflict, and a lead character whose destiny shifts the balance between Heaven and Hell.

🎬 Edge of the Block (series) —
Urban, gritty, raw, perfect for a streaming series or limited-run Netflix-style drama.

🎬 No Mercy Left, The Last Revelation, The Final Prophecy —
End-times thrillers with cinematic visuals, spiritual depth, and blockbuster potential.

These aren’t “ideas.”
These are published works, already moving thousands of readers — stories built with character arcs, emotional weight, and world-building filmmakers dream about.

I’m looking for the RIGHT partner:
👉 A producer with vision
👉 A director who loves building new worlds
👉 An indie studio hungry for original IP
👉 Someone who wants to turn books into films with real impact

If you’re interested in reading the logline, synopsis, or treatment — or if you’re a filmmaker who loves collaborating with authors — comment below or DM me directly.

Let’s build something legendary.
Let’s create a film people will feel, not just watch.

— Jerry Valentino Wright
Author | Creator | Visionary Storyteller

items.text:
🎭 **CASTING CALL — VLYT ART SCENE STUDY**

Project: *De Nieuwe Ridderorde* — *Temperance Knights*

Format: Recorded Scene Study + Showcase Screening

Language: English & Afrikaans (Dutch if requested)

Location: Pretoria & Online

Showcase: February 2026

Vlyt Art Acting invites actors to participate in a first-of-its-kind scene study of De Nieuwe Ridderorde — an 1800s Cape satire by Charles Boniface.

Disclaimer: This is not a paid gig. It is a proof-of-concept project designed to create recorded and live-streamed scene study content. Actors will gain professional footage, exposure, and experience with rare material.

What makes this special:

✔️ Humorous, political satire from early Cape literature

✔️ Multi-character ensemble scenes

✔️ Physical comedy, heightened language, and character archetypes

✔️ Material never translated/performed in contemporary South Africa

**ROLES AVAILABLE**

(All genders considered, age flexible)

**TEMPERANCE KNIGHTS** – The “sober” order who are secretly drunk

 • Domine Humbug Philippumpkin (Reverend Humbug, pompous commander)

 • Stoeleman Puff (Chairman Puff, blustering vice-president)

 • Sir John Brute (Banner-bearer, strict but drunk)

 • Delirium Tremens (Head medic, comically afflicted by alcohol-related madness)

**NEWLY-INDUCTED KNIGHTS** – Comedic, physical roles

 • Manus Kalkfachter (Bethelsdorp representative, “sheep follower”)

 • Griet Drilbouten (Disruptive wife, hiding/spying, comic physicality)

 • Klaas Galgevogel (“Gallows Bird,” comedic nickname)

 • Piet Dronkelap (“Drunken Flap,” comic drunken knight)

**ANTI-TEMPERANCE GROUP — THE COGNAC DRINKERS** – sharp-witted satirical commentators

 • Quizz (Cunning lawyer)

 • O’Candid (Gruff old soldier)

 • Dr Macthirsty (Phrenologist, parody scientist)

 • Call-His-Son (Jolly brandy distiller)

**PROJECT DETAILS**

• Commitment: 4 rehearsals + final recorded/live session

• Tone: Satire, physical comedy, ensemble chaos

• Actor Benefits: First-ever classical South African text on reel, professional recording footage, live-stream exposure

**INTERESTED? APPLY HERE:**

👉 https://forms.gle/VBvoxiskNvudAngx8

sharedPost.text:
Vlyt Art Scene Study is a space where actors work with classic South African theatre — from 1800s Cape satire to folk theatre, Voortrekker epics, and old Boer dramas.

This round we’re exploring De Nieuwe Ridderorde (1832), a Cape Town satire in the style of French Comédie, exposing a “temperance” order who are secretly drunk behind closed doors.

To apply, use the link in bio. #vlytartacting #casting #scenestudy #actorslife

Happy Tuesday all!

I provide an affordable PAY WHAT YOU CAN showreel service for new or established actors/directors/cinematographers/comedians/hobbyists etc 

Please see samples of recent clients in the link below 😎

I'm an actor myself so I know how frustrating it can be, especially when you're starting out, to collate your footage together to get more work, without wanting to spend a fortune. 

Basically, send me your footage (or I can try and source it for you online if it's commercially aired) and I shall edit it together into a lovely reel.

For any further info / enquiries / to book my services, drop me an email and I'll respond as quick as I can:

reelsforanyone@gmail.com

I'll look forward to hearing from you.

Thanks! 

😎

🌍 **You're Invited: Alex Fil's 27th Birthday Bash in Covent Garden – I'm Alone in the UK & Need Your Company! 🎂✨**

Hey London (and world wanderers)! I'm Alex Fil – Ukrainian TV presenter living my London adventure **but completely alone here, with no one to celebrate my birthday with**. Turning 27 on **28 November at 7:30 PM** – join me for an open, fun-filled evening at **Apple Market, Covent Garden (WC2E 8RF)**!

I'll bring some cake & drinks to share, but since **I have no friends or family nearby** (and don't know who's coming!), bring your faves: snacks, bubbly, balloons, or just your amazing self. Let's turn my lonely day into a pop-up party under the market lights – good vibes, stories, and maybe a spontaneous sing-along? 😊

**RSVP: Comment below or DM me!** Tag friends who can make a stranger's day. #CoventGardenParty #LondonBirthdayBash #AloneInUK #BringYourVibes

🎬 **CASTING CALL – SOCIAL MEDIA CAMPAIGN (PAID)**
Casting multiple lifestyle roles for a social media video campaign shot in Johannesburg / Pretoria. All roles are paid. Seeking authentic talent with real, natural energy.

📅 **Production Date:** Late November 2025 (exact dates TBC)
⏳ **Submission Deadline:** ASAP
📍 **Location:** Johannesburg / Pretoria, South Africa
💰 **Pay:** Paid (rates discussed upon selection)
🏷 **Union Status:** Not Applicable
🎥 **Production Type:** Social Media Campaign

---

### **ROLES AVAILABLE**

🎭 **Braai Host (30–55, any gender)**
Warm, relatable South African energy. Must be comfortable prepping food, handling braai grid/tongs, and interacting naturally in a backyard scene.

🎣 **River Angler (28–50, any gender)**
Outdoorsy and calm. Should be comfortable mimicking fly-fishing movements and walking on uneven riverbank terrain.

🥾 **Hiker / Camper (20–35, any gender)**
Active, capable vibe. Will tie guylines, prep kindling, and perform light camp tasks in a scenic ridge/tent scene.

🚜 **Farmer / Farmhand (30–65, any gender)**
Authentic rural presence. Will appear in a field/shed scene doing light fence work, twine cutting, or walking crop rows.

---

### **SUBMISSION REQUIREMENTS**

📸 Headshot (natural light)
📷 Full-length photo
🖐 Hands close-ups (front & back)
🎥 20–30 sec video: State name, height, and languages spoken
🗣 Languages: English + any of Afrikaans, isiZulu, isiXhosa, or Sesotho (please indicate fluency)
📅 Confirm availability for late November
⚠️ Disclose any current commercial conflicts (e.g. food, outdoor, tools brands)

---

📩 **HOW TO APPLY**
Apply as a Talent PRO member via Actors and Extras with a **1-month FREE trial**:
🌐 [https://actorsandextras.com/casting-calls](https://actorsandextras.com/casting-calls)

Create your free profile and **GET NOTIFIED** of new roles in your area.
Join [www.actorsandextras.com](http://www.actorsandextras.com) today.

---

🔍 *This casting has been shared by Actors and Extras as a service to our talent directory members. We have received permission to share it and believe it to be legitimate. However, we strongly encourage all applicants to exercise due diligence and independently verify the details of the project before proceeding.*

#actorsandextras #actorlife #castingcall #southafricaactors

Zwischen Rückblicken und Gegenwart erzählt Angelina von ihrer Sucht, die Suche nach sich selbst. Paul Komparse 23 Jahre alt männlich braune Haare keine Erfahrung nötig Ärtztin Komparsin 50 Jahre alt weiblich braun/graue Haare keine Erfahrung nötig Bewerbung unter: gierlinger. gierlnger.hanna@ortweinschule.at Bewerbungsunterlagen: Bewerbungsvideo Lebenslauf Bewerbungsfrist: 7.12 2025 Drehtermin: 19.3. 22.3. 2025 in Graz Ein Projekt der HTBLVA Graz Ortweinschule.'

items.text:
**Raum Rheinland | Freundinnen-Paar zum Thema Geschenke für TV-Beitrag gesucht**

** **

Für einen TV-Beitrag des Magazins „Life“ suchen wir zwei Freundinnen, die im Rheinland zuhause sind. Gemeinsam mit euch wollen wir testen, welche Methode das beste Geschenk für die Person an eurer Seite hervorbringt: eure eigene Idee, die Empfehlung einer Expertin oder der Vorschlag einer KI.

 

Im Experiment überlegt ihr euch zunächst jeweils ein Geschenk füreinander. Danach besprecht ihr eure Ideen mit einer Expertin, die ebenfalls ein Geschenk für die andere Person entwickelt. Zum Abschluss tritt eine KI an – und wir schauen, welches Geschenk am Ende am meisten überzeugt.

 

Ihr habt Lust mitzumachen und herauszufinden, womit ihr der anderen Person die größte Freude machen könnt? Dann schreibt mir einfach eine Nachricht :)

Freue mich auf eure Nachrichten!

Der Kino Mittwoch auf radioYpsilon 

MOVIETIME KW 47/2025

DIE RÜCKKEHR INS ZAUBERHAFTE LAND, WEIHNACHTSFILME UND KLIMASCHUTZ

Nach 1 Jahr warten folgt nun die Rückkehr in die zauberhafte Welt von Oz. Eines der Kinohighlights 2025 ist nun zu sehen, WICKED: FOR GOOD ist gleich in mehreren Kinos zu bewundern (Stadtkinocenter Laa,  Babylon Kino Horn und Filmbühne Waidhofen/Ybbs).

Nebst der Kinoadaption seines Kabarettprogrammes AUFPUTZT IS (Stadtkino Horn), konnten wir mit Gery Seidl ein spezielles Interview führen. 

In eisige Welten führt uns Nicolas Geyrhalter mit seiner Doku MELT. Über die Entstehung dieses Filmes und was das Thema Umweltschutz damit zu tun hat, erzählt der Regisseur im Gespräch mit uns.

Weitere Filmtipps und Musik fast ausschließlich aus den beiden WICKED Filmen präsentiert Ihnen Sarah Fuchs.

Mittwoch 19.11.25 von 18 bis 19h auf radioYpsilon 94.5 oder via Stream (http://mp3.radioypsilon.at:8000/)

items.text: Attention filmmakers and creatives: don't miss this networking event on December 6th, at Red Leg Brewing Company in Colorado Springs! This is your chance to connect directly with the region's best directors, producers, cinematographers, and artists to find the missing piece for your next film or media project. This is where you access local opportunities and build a strong professional network while enjoying great brews in the Pikes Peak region. RSVP now and be a part of the vibrant Colorado creative community!

items.text:
CASTING CALL - INDEPENDENT FEATURE FILM (UNPAID)

Production Type: Independent Feature Film
Location: Fairplay, Colorado 
Compensation: Unpaid
Union Status: Non-Union
Filming Window: December 8th to December 11th. 

We are currently casting two male roles for an upcoming feature film. No plot or story details will be released publicly at this stage.

---

ROLE 1 - OLIVER

Gender: Male
Age Range: Late 20s - Early 30s
Height: 5'8" - 6'0"
Role Type: Speaking Role

Basic Description:

A kind, charming, deeply devoted man. Soft-spoken, loyal, and emotionally open. Requires strong emotional delivery and gentle romantic energy.

---

ROLE 2 - ROWAN

Gender: Male
Age Range: 20s
Height: 6'0" - 6'5"
Hair: Brown hair required
Role Type: Speaking Role

Basic Description:
A confident, flirty, golden-retriever-energy type. Playful, bold, and naturally dominant in presence and personality. Requires strong charisma, smooth delivery, and comfortable flirtation.

---

TO SUBMIT:

Email hallowphoriaproductions@outlook.com
 with:
• Headshot
• Full body photo
• Height + age
• Resume (if you have one)
• Reel OR a short introduction video

Subject line:
“CASTING - [Role Name]”

---

NOTES:

• All info about the film will be shared privately after audition selection.
• Must be local or able to commute to filming location.
• Non-union actors preferred

Happy Auditioning!✨️

Gender: Male
Age Range: 20s
Height: 6'0" - 6'5"
Hair: Brown hair required
Role Type: Speaking Role

Basic Description:
A confident, flirty, golden-retriever-energy type. Playful, bold, and naturally dominant in presence and personality. Requires strong charisma, smooth delivery, and comfortable flirtation.

---

TO SUBMIT:

Email hallowphoriaproductions@outlook.com
 with:
• Headshot
• Full body photo
• Height + age
• Resume (if you have one)
• Reel OR a short introduction video

Subject line:
“CASTING - [Role Name]”

---

NOTES:

• All info about the film will be shared privately after audition selection.
• Must be local or able to commute to filming location.
• Non-union actors preferred

Happy Auditioning!✨️

items.text:
**CASTING CALL **

Hey, wir suchen Schauspieler*innen für unseren Low-Budget-Studenten-Kurzfilm. Bei Interesse kontaktiert uns bitte per E-Mail: **[LivShortfilm2026@gmail.com](mailto:LivShortfilm2026@gmail.com)**.

Der Film wird an verschiedenen Locations gedreht, daher solltet ihr über einen längeren Zeitraum (**mindestens eine Woche am Stück**) verfügbar sein. 

**Unterkünfte, Anfahrt und Verpflegung werden gestellt.**

** **

** **

**Gesucht wird:**

 

**Männlich gelesene Person (Schauspieler*in)**

20-35 Jahre alt

**Voraussetzungen:**
* Autoführerschein
* Deutsche Sprache C1

 

**Drehort:**

Primär Münster NRW

 

**Drehtage:**

7 Drehtage zwischen dem 07. und 16. Januar

 

**Handlung:**

Die Sängerin Liv kämpft mit ihrer stagnierenden Karriere. Nachdem sie vor einem ihrer Auftritte zusammengebrochen ist, nimmt sie sich eine Auszeit mit ihrem Freund.

Während er glaubt, ihren Traum zu retten, versucht sie, sich von dem zu befreien, was aus diesem Traum geworden ist.

**Wir freuen uns über alle Bewerbungen!**

Januar STORY: Die Sängerin Liv kämpft mit ihrer stagnie agnierenden enden Karriere, Nachdem sie vor einem ihrer Auftritte zusammen- gebrochen ist, nimmt sie sich eine Auszeit mit ihrem Freund, Während er glaubt, ihren Traum zu retten, versucht sie, sich von demn zu befreien, was aus diesem Traum geworden ist,'

items.text:
*Michael Chekhov Europe* invites you to its first workshop in the new year: 

**THE MOVING SPACE: Atmosphere and Playfulness on Stage **

with **David Zinder**, Tel Aviv, **Vladimir Baicher**, Moscow, **Suzana Nikolić**, Zagreb, **Ulrich Meyer-Horsch**, Hamburg

**January 29 to February 1, 2026 **in Hamburg, Germany 

The space on stage is full of life, full of energy and breath. All an actor has to do is connect to this living space. 

What happens when we dive into the world of a given play and allow ourselves to be surprised by its specific dynamics, energy, language and space? 

Michael Chekhov’s concepts of “Atmosphere” (“the soul of every performance”) and “The Feeling of Ease, Form, Beauty and the Whole” will guide us through this exploration. 

*Movement in Space – Objective Atmosphere – Spatial Relationship – Personal Atmosphere – Feeling of Ease, Form, Beauty and the Whole – Organic breathing – Playfulness – Ensemble *

Michael Chekhov Europe Training – module 2

Tuition fee: 450€ / 490€

More information: [[https://sfsh.de/michael-chekhov-module-2/sfsh10037/](https://sfsh.de/michael-chekhov-module-2/sfsh10037/?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQQMjIyMDM5MTc4ODIwMDg5MghjYWxsc2l0ZQEyAAEeY52GI3lQe3pjPHhDXowpGuLqIQrzJcqGyZcZh3SR3jGKGPx3ohVQgDBpaaY_aem_LqlofjR6f5SXrNzWnHvQPg&brid=aB9vxtDqrKES53cnQp0y_A)](https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsfsh.de%2Fmichael-chekhov-module-2%2Fsfsh10037%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQQMjIyMDM5MTc4ODIwMDg5MghjYWxsc2l0ZQEyAAEex7NVSBwXFESZYv0PnNVOZZnSrzpDqZTYYyPIFJFP5nZT3Q26Ztt6WS-2fEA_aem_avdglXTU1DOTHvEm2ODLWw%26brid%3DkHUv4f1OfBXrKWr9lBtxHA&h=AT3aprJLj6mz3iCe_wMtmzrhtZGIayz1KSnpU58Ex7Z3EzPlrdAAC1KuqKpynOGfS5EK5Ig9QN83EuaeroAfCpArCXGbw_dimFyj16sIOeaPH6rPkuzKw_HUwj0Asyp3ugyfD65FobRJTmjdHtFUjy3Q2Q&__tn__=-UK-R&c[0]=AT0HA0NarzIKKHpcfuGCk_r7lozXPeUvPcNPcopwlZ-UI1byChoQ3du3h8W5ximHzMBhAEXGkb_bl8TQatSz2VHJa7jDl-KVLtmeALpkJ1DA_bE9mEexuYkjuWUew5yTen0VdKvkkNsZpaSC4X3beQM387ABsSrCYXTYojujQlQB)

Contact: chekhov@sfsh.de 

This in-person workshop can be acknowledged as part of the upcoming MICHA/MCE Teachers Training.

items.text:
The end of the year has a way of sneaking up on us.
And then you start reflecting on what you thought would look different by now.
It’s all part of the creative cycle; Some years build us, some years stretch us. 

And some years just leave us asking, “Okay, what now?” 🫤

If you’re ready to stop waiting for change and actually *create it* in 2026, check this out:

My friend Jodie Bentley is hosting a **free 3-day event for actors and creatives** called **Be Unstoppable: Rewire Your Mindset. Design Your Year. 💪🏻🔥**

It’s designed to help you:
 ✅ Let go of what’s been weighing you down
 ✅ Reconnect to what you truly want
 ✅ Build a plan that actually works for your creative life

If you’re craving clarity and momentum, this is your sign.
Register here: [https://bit.ly/3LQjWpB](https://bit.ly/3LQjWpB)

items.text:
Actors… your passion is entertaining people — yet you’re not creating any content. Naughty. 👿

You want auditions?
You want an agent?
You want a career?

Then stop hiding.

Casting directors are online. Audiences are online. The actors getting the roles are online.

If you’re not creating content, you’re invisible.
Invisible actors don’t get work.

Fix it. Today. 👿🔥

message.text:
Actors… your passion is entertaining people — yet you’re not creating any content. Naughty. 👿

You want auditions?
You want an agent?
You want a career?

Then stop hiding.

Casting directors are online. Audiences are online. The actors getting the roles are online.

If you’re not creating content, you’re invisible.
Invisible actors don’t get work.

Fix it. Today. 👿🔥

👉 linktr.ee/mattzina

items.text:
🔥 ATTENTION FILMMAKERS, DIRECTORS & INDIE PRODUCERS 🔥

My name is Jerry Valentino Wright — published author of 11 books and creator of multiple cinematic universes that are READY to be adapted to film.

I’m seeking one serious, visionary producer or small production company who sees potential where others see limits — someone who wants to help bring a powerful, original franchise to life.

I have several finished books that are visually explosive, emotionally gripping, and built for the screen, including:

🎬 The Eternal War: Light vs Darkness —
A supernatural action-drama with apocalyptic tension, angelic warfare, moral conflict, and a lead character whose destiny shifts the balance between Heaven and Hell.

🎬 Edge of the Block (series) —
Urban, gritty, raw, perfect for a streaming series or limited-run Netflix-style drama.

🎬 No Mercy Left, The Last Revelation, The Final Prophecy —
End-times thrillers with cinematic visuals, spiritual depth, and blockbuster potential.

These aren’t “ideas.”
These are published works, already moving thousands of readers — stories built with character arcs, emotional weight, and world-building filmmakers dream about.

I’m looking for the RIGHT partner:
👉 A producer with vision
👉 A director who loves building new worlds
👉 An indie studio hungry for original IP
👉 Someone who wants to turn books into films with real impact

If you’re interested in reading the logline, synopsis, or treatment — or if you’re a filmmaker who loves collaborating with authors — comment below or DM me directly.

Let’s build something legendary.
Let’s create a film people will feel, not just watch.

— Jerry Valentino Wright
Author | Creator | Visionary Storyteller

Hi everyone! JC here, Mia Maree’s assistant. 💛
We’re raising support for Mia’s $50K Comeback Campaign as she prepares for her big return — including her upcoming debut at LA Fashion Week and continued work with Women in Power TV.

Every share or donation truly helps Mia rebuild the brand with purpose and empower more women through fashion and storytelling.

Support the campaign here:

Thank you so much for the love and support. 🙏✨

items.text:
Casting Call for Short 10-15 minutes called Repossession 

This is a  darkly comic short about ambition, fame, and the unexpected horrors lurking behind a routine job.

Casting call for the characters 
Kyle
 A seasoned presenter clinging to relevance in a changing media landscape. Desperate for a comeback, he takes one last job—blinded by ambition, even when the warning signs turn supernatural.
 Playing Age: Early 30s to mid 40s
 Ethnicity: Any
 Gender: Male
Spencer
 Kyle’s loyal second-in-command, tasked with shaping the show’s content. Often dragged into eerie locations, Spencer must confront whether he’s valued as a partner—or just a pawn.
 Playing Age: Mid 20s to Mid 30s
 Ethnicity: Any
 Gender: Male
Carla Curses
 A flashy social media psychic with a massive following and a hunger for viral fame. Her pursuit of a haunted object leads to possession—transforming her into something savage and inhuman.
 Playing Age: 20s to 30s
 Ethnicity: Any
 Gender: Female
Frank
Carla’s trusted cameraman, now shattered by the night’s horrors. Haunted and fragile, his trauma slowly pulls him into the house’s darkness.
Playing Age: 30s to 40s
Ethnicity: Any
Physicality: Tall and lanky
Gender: Male

Filming will take place in the Liverpool/Merseyside area, United Kingdom. Looking to film middle to end of January 2026 
Please apply only if you're based locally.
For more details, contact: houndsoftheroundtable@gmail.com

Please note we do not reply to comments or direct Facebook messages. Thank you!

items.text:
My name is Jerry Valentino Wright — published author of 11 books and creator of multiple cinematic universes that are READY to be adapted to film.

I’m seeking one serious, visionary producer or small production company who sees potential where others see limits — someone who wants to help bring a powerful, original franchise to life.

I have several finished books that are visually explosive, emotionally gripping, and built for the screen, including:

🎬 The Eternal War: Light vs Darkness —
A supernatural action-drama with apocalyptic tension, angelic warfare, moral conflict, and a lead character whose destiny shifts the balance between Heaven and Hell.

🎬 Edge of the Block (series) —
Urban, gritty, raw, perfect for a streaming series or limited-run Netflix-style drama.

🎬 No Mercy Left, The Last Revelation, The Final Prophecy —
End-times thrillers with cinematic visuals, spiritual depth, and blockbuster potential.

These aren’t “ideas.”
These are published works, already moving thousands of readers — stories built with character arcs, emotional weight, and world-building filmmakers dream about.

I’m looking for the RIGHT partner:
👉 A producer with vision
👉 A director who loves building new worlds
👉 An indie studio hungry for original IP
👉 Someone who wants to turn books into films with real impact

If you’re interested in reading the logline, synopsis, or treatment — or if you’re a filmmaker who loves collaborating with authors — comment below or DM me directly.

Let’s build something legendary.
Let’s create a film people will feel, not just watch.

— Jerry Valentino Wright
Author | Creator | Visionary Storyteller

📅 21 November | 12:00 PM | North Hollywood
✨ Only 20 participants - selective casting.

We - a partner of TikTok, Entertainment Agency - are filming a professional educational course on TikTok Live Sales.
We are currently selecting students who will:
🎓 appear on camera as the classroom audience
📘 and simultaneously receive real training in TikTok Live Sales techniques.

What you will gain:
• Practical skills for working in TikTok Live
• A clear understanding of how a selling livestream is structured
• The possibility of being included in the exclusive creator pool of our agency, working in a professional studio equipped for TikTok livestreams
• Possible access to various projects within our agency
• The opportunity to work with exclusive products
• $60 for participating in the filming day

Why this opportunity is valuable:
• This is a real chance to enter the TikTok Live Commerce industry.
• Participants go through a selection process - we choose motivated, attentive, and standout individuals.
• Filming takes place in a studio format. Please come in a neat yet bright look. Charismatic outfits are very welcome.

📞 To apply, please send:
 1. Your photos
 2. Your TikTok account
via Telegram / WhatsApp / Messenger: 747-286-83-92 Karina

Experience is not required - what matters is respect for the process, interest in the industry, and the desire to grow.

Grupa studentów I roku Szkoły Filmowej w Łodzi poszukuje mieszkania (w Łodzi), do  realizacji  krótkiego filmu ćwiczeniowego, realizowanego w ramach zajęć.

Zależy nam na pokoju (sypialnia nastoletniej bohaterki), przedpokoju i drugim pokoju  lub łazience. Mieszkanie w bloku, nowe budownictwo, nowsze meble.
Super gdyby ściany były różowe/błękitne,  niekoniecznie białe.
Najwięcej prac scenograficznych planujemy w sypialni.
Projekt ma charakter non-profit z racji, że jako studenci dysponujemy bardzo skromnym budżetem. Możemy jedynie zaproponować symboliczną zapłatę.

items.text:
Title: Exit Game

Genre: adventure/horror/

Laughter echoed and glasses clinked as five friends, bathed in the warm glow of camaraderie and a couple of celebratory drinks, scrolled through late-night ads until an intriguing "puzzle room expedition" caught their collective eye. Spurred by a mix of alcohol-fueled bravado and genuine curiosity, they booked the ultimate test of wits, little realizing that their spontaneous decision would plunge them into an unimaginable horror. The simulated challenge quickly morphed into a horrifying nightmare as they found themselves not in a cleverly designed game, but genuinely trapped within the cold, cavernous confines of an industrial warehouse. Each "puzzle" was revealed to be a meticulously crafted deathtrap—lethal gas, crushing walls, and razor-sharp lasers awaiting their every misstep. Now sobered by sheer terror, can this quintet decipher the intricate, deadly mechanisms of their elaborate prison and find the elusive path to freedom, or will their impromptu adventure turn into their final, fatal escape.

Location : Birmingham, West midlands 

Male: Alec Campbell (19-30)

Male: Mitchell Saunders (19-30)

Male: Kyle Edmunds (19-30)

Female: Jessica Reid (19-30)

Female: Amy Henderson (19-30)

Paid work : £600 Per person 

Accommodation and travel expenses paid for. 

Date: TBC

We’re casting for Plus One, a soulful indie film about connection in a digital world. Shooting Dec 9th -16th. PAID roles – Indie role, non-union welcome. Seeking talented actors for Marcus Kane and Samson Adeyemi roles. 

📍 Location: Denver, CO
📩 Submit headshot & resume: taboomediagroup@gmail.com
Subject line: Samson – Plus One Submission

Selected applicants will receive sides and self-tape instructions.

Email headshot & resume to taboomediagroup@gmail.com with subject line: Role Name – Plus One Submission. Let’s make something unforgettable. Denver Area.

attachments.ocrText: May be an image of text that says 'CASTING CALL FEATURE FILM PLUS ONE ROLES SEEKING SAMSON ADEYEMI Male, Black, late 40s-50s. Elegant, introspective, quietly powerful. MARCUS KANE Male, 30s-40s Flashy, confident, and manipulative influencer. Self-styled branding guru; charismatic, loud, with a sharp comedic edge. Think intense 'manfluencer' meets high-energy motivational speaker. co LOCATION: Denver, TO SUBMIT: Email headshot & resume to taboomediagroup@gmail.com Subject line: [ROLE NAME] -Plus One Submission Selected applicants will receive sides and self-tape instructions.'

Das 13 Seitige Manifest über Schauspielrei
# **MANIFEST DES SCHAUSPIELERS

Der Bote zwischen den Welten**
## **1. Präambel – Das Erwachen des Schauspielers**

Ich bin Schauspieler. **Shogun Peter Lakshmi a.d.H. Wehrli**
Doch ich bin mehr als ein Darsteller, mehr als ein Körper auf einer Bühne.
Ich bin ein Resonanzraum, ein Spiegel der Zeit, ein Träger von Botschaften.
Ich betrete nicht Rollen –
ich betrete Realitäten.

**Meine Aufgabe ist nicht, zu imitieren.**
**Meine Aufgabe ist, zu *****offenbaren*****.**

Wenn ich spreche,
spreche ich nicht nur Worte –
ich öffne Tore.

**Wenn ich spiele,**
**spiele ich nicht nur Figuren –**
**ich bewege Bewusstsein.**

**weiter lesen unter diesem Link**

https://diegoldenezeit-shogunwehrli.jimdofree.com/das-golden-zeitalter/

🎙✨ Singing Chansons across borders – in English, French, and German – with a view that says it all:
🌊 Endless horizons, blue in blue...
The sea reflects what’s inside us — calm, deep, vast.

When I sing, I open windows to emotions, stories, languages.
When you listen… maybe you see your own horizons too.

Take that feeling home. Let it echo.

Soon performing in Australia

items.text:
Hello, im currently looking for collaborators for a documentary Film project. 

I would like to find ppl to work on a music documentary to the topic of Post-Punk music with a focus on the contemporary scene, its developing in the last 2 decades, the influence it has on the Mainstream music and the challenges it has in the current music industry. The documentary should introduce many of the upcoming underground artists, same as show the different sides of the music and touring live, explain aspects from the musician, label and promoter side. 

Its a long idea of mine i would to contribute. 

Little to myself. 

Im a concert promoter, booker, musician, DJ active since ca 20 Years in the Post-Punk scene, with thousands of shows and events produced and worked with most of the currently active artists in the scene. As i use to film the concerts, i also have hundreds of shows filmed which i would like to contribute to the project, same as background infos, personal contacts, interviews and much more. 

As Post-Punk is one of the currently most growing and influential genres in the last 15 years of underground music, this topic should also interest many. Beside introducing the documenting the development and artists, i also would like to show insights in the live and carrier of musicians and share some knowhow. 

I hope to find ppl here who would like to work on this project with me. I also hope that the result will find a wide interested audience.

We are looking for expressive, friendly, and photogenic Berliners who are ready to be part of something innovative! Join us in front of the green screen for four hours and we'll transform you into a digital AI-avatar, to help our users explain complex topics, provide customer support, and engage with people around the world.

Send us your headshots and we’ll give you more information about this project, the casting process, and our projected filming dates later this year. 

No acting experience required. Compensation: €500. 

Contact casting@simpleshow.com to get the process started today!

–DE– 

Wir suchen ausdrucksstarke, freundliche und fotogene Berliner:innen, die Lust haben, Teil von etwas Innovativem zu werden! Komm für vier Stunden vor unseren Greenscreen und wir verwandeln dich in einen digitalen, KI-Avatar, der unseren Nutzern hilft, komplexe Themen zu erklären, Kund:innen zu unterstützen und Menschen auf der ganzen Welt zu erreichen.

Schick uns deine Headshots und wir geben dir alle weiteren Infos zu diesem Projekt, zum Casting-Prozess und zu den geplanten Drehtagen Ende dieses Monats oder Anfang Dezember.

Schauspielerfahrung ist nicht erforderlich. Vergütung: 500 €.

Kontakt casting@simpleshow.com und starte noch heute den Prozess!

items.text:
CASTING CALL FOR NEW PLAY!
--------------------------------

A New Comedic play by Zack Faulks, *Bulimia is My Roman Empire* follows a group of Servants as they attempt to assassinate the Emperor. They discover that power may not be all that they had once desired. Learning that their target is engaged in a number of self-destructive behaviours, our conspirators are forced to follow down a long rabbit hole of strange diets, machismo, and fascism should they want to prove that they deserve the right to rule. As a satire of manhood, ultimately no one’s happy with where they end up.

For more information check out the images below!

Deadline to submit is Nov. 29, 2025 at 12:00pm.

--------------------
Find us at www.greattrashproductions.ca

items.text:
Casting Call (Non-Union) for COUPLES - Paid

Looking for actors to play the role of clients in a simulated therapy session. The video clips will be used in an online training system for counselors and psychologists. The sessions include some scripted elements to prepare, and then some improv with prompts.

We are currently interested in filming with mature couples, queer couples, interracial couples, or throuples/polycules of various gender identity combinations. All ages, all gender expressions/identities, all ethnicities, and persons with disabilities are welcome. 

All experience levels with acting are welcome, including experienced actors with less experienced partners. We are committed to making this a respectful and safe process, with open communication and respect for boundaries.

Comfortable English fluency is required.

Immediate filming dates are November 14 to 18, based on actor availability, but more will occur in the future so please submit if you're interested at all.

Location is downtown Vancouver - Gastown. Pay is $90 CAD per performer, with the expectation of some prepared material, studio session duration: 1 hour

Please email phil@skillsetter.com with your headshot and resume, as well as some information about you and your partner, such as gender identities, age, cultural/racial backgrounds. If you've submitted for a past session, you're welcome to submit again. We do sometimes receive more submissions than we are able to respond to, but we do read them all, and we do save your submissions for future consideration.

Egy Kanadában készülő játékfilm meghitt karácsonyi jelenetéhez keresünk 2 hegedűst, 1 brácsást és 1 csellistát, akik egy elegáns hotel ünnepi környezetében adnának elő egy gyönyörű karácsonyi dalt.
A jelenet hangulata bensőséges, elegáns és ünnepi – ezért kifejezetten olyan zenészek jelentkezését várjuk, akik magabiztosan és igényesen zenélnek kamera előtt is.

📅 Forgatási időszak: december 1–19.
A részvétel 1–2 napot vesz igénybe.
💸 Kiemelt díjazás, professzionális csapat és felejthetetlen élmény!

📩 Jelentkezés: info@ninecasting.hu

• egy friss fotót magadról

items.text:
Reposting because lead actor dropped out!

DRAMA SHORT FILM CASTING CALL – In His Care

SYNOPSIS: When granddaughter, Red, stops receiving letters from her sick grandmother she insists on visiting. Surprised, she finds a man who claims to be her grandmother’s new carer. As he continues to ask strange questions and refuses to let Red see her, she realises the man is taking advantage of her poor grandmother, using medicines to make her sicker. When confronted the man becomes enraged and is forced to kill little Red. 

Wanted: 1 actors (F) for exciting new short film ‘In His Care’. Shooting in Hertfordshire, w/c 24th November, student project from an award-winning Film & TV course.

- RED (Female, 24 – 30)

- Description: Mid to late 20s

Red is a simple, reserved girl. She is kind and holds herself highly. But when it comes to her grandma, she is extremely protective, fierce even. She is perceptive and head strong and will do anything to find what’s happening at grandma’s house.

- Height: 5’5 – 5’9

- Appearance: Red is a modest girl. She dresses simple when visiting her grandmother, always wearing the infamous red scarf that her grandmother gave her.

- Travel Expenses / Food Paid

please contact sheldonkieran4@gmail.com

The end of the year has a way of sneaking up on us.
And then you start reflecting on what you thought would look different by now.
It’s all part of the creative cycle; Some years build us, some years stretch us. 

And some years just leave us asking, “Okay, what now?” 🫤

If you’re ready to stop waiting for change and actually *create it* in 2026, check this out:

My friend Jodie Bentley is hosting a **free 3-day event for actors and creatives** called **Be Unstoppable: Rewire Your Mindset. Design Your Year. 💪🏻🔥**

It’s designed to help you:
 ✅ Let go of what’s been weighing you down
 ✅ Reconnect to what you truly want
 ✅ Build a plan that actually works for your creative life

If you’re craving clarity and momentum, this is your sign.
Register here: [https://bit.ly/3LQjWpB](https://bit.ly/3LQjWpB)

sharedPost.text:
+++ Was erlauben" Constantin? +++
Eine Chronologie sozialer Kälte

Auch die Mallorca Zeitung berichtet

Kinoproduktion "Der perfekte Urlaub" 

Okt. Nov. 
Auf Mallorca gesuchte Komparsen (überwiegend intern. Touristen) bekommen  82.50 EUR Brutto pro Nachtdreh (bei 5 Drehtagen,10.11.-14.11) je 10 Std. Arbeit + 1Std.Pause
(Abrechnung n. Mindestlohn, Spanien)

6.Nov.
Constantin Film sucht (scheinbar aus der Not) nun auch  kurzfristig aus Deutschland Komparsen incl. Übernachtungsmöglichkeit
 jedoch OHNE Gage, Nachtzulage und  Flugkostenerstattung für 5 Drehnächte
 (s. Online-Gesuch 
(Faire Gagen berichtete)

Nach massiver Kritik vieler Filmschaffender  und auch unser Initiative "Faire Gagen":
Umstrittenes Gesuch wird von Constantin Film kommentarlos gelöscht. 

08.Nov.
Constantin Film sucht wiederum in Deutschland Komparsen für brsagte 5 Drehnächte nun  MIT Flugkostenübernahme und 50.00 EUR  Aufwandsentschädigung (Gage) diesmal via Agentur Producer's Friend.

"Faire Gagen" fordert dennoch respektvolle Gagen nach dem in Deutschland geltenden gesetzlichen Mindestlohn  einer Nachtzulage und eine  Gleichbehandlung  ALLER  Komparsen am Set via "Offenen Brief" 

"Mallorca Zeitung" (MZ) fragt daraufhin ebenfalls kritisch nach.

Antwort Constantin Film an MZ:  "Die aus Deutschland eingeflogenen Komparsen bekommen selbstverständlich den in Deutschland üblichen Mindestlohn mit Nachtzulage und  auch die Flugkosten-Erstattung (s. Beitrag aus der MZ)

19.Nov. 14.45h
Die Initiative "Faire Gagen" hat trotz Offenen Brief und nochmaliger Bitte, kein Statement und  damit auch keinerlei Erklärung oder Entschuldigung für die vielen irritierten und verärgerten Filmschaffenden  von Constantin Film erhalten.

Dazu die Fälle der Vergangenheit bei ebenfalls großen Kinoproduktionen mit den Versuchen bei  hunderten  Komparsen den deutschen Mindestlohn zu umgehen  den wir jedoch ebenfalls durchsetzen konnten.
(Faire Gagen berichtete)

Was bleibt ist ein respektloses Durcheinander mit immer wieder verärgerten, verprellten und verwunderten Komparsen und der Frage: 

"Warum Constantin Film  gerade im eh schon schlecht bezahlten Filmgewerk Komparserie und  Kleindarstellerei wiederholt den  z.T. auch gesetzeswidrigen Rotstift ansetzt?"

Die Initiative Faire Gagen und damit  unsere, weiter zunehmende Anhängerschaft, wird diesen Weg keinesfalls mitgehen und weiterhin offen, den Finger in die Wunde legen.

Zudem fordern wir eine Gleichbehandlung der Filmschaffenden am gemeinsamen Set und dulden keine Zweiklassengesellschaft.

Filmschaffende aber auch ganz besonders Filmfans fordern wir auf, genau hinzusehen wenn es um eine verdiente Gage und den respektvollen Umgang geht.

Auch daher unsere aktuelle Aktion:
Hände weg von miesen Gagen.
Siehe Faire Gagen.

+++ Und wie immer die Bitte auf die derzeit besonders wichtigen Beiträge, Reaktionen zeigen, da textlastige Beiträge in der Regel 
etwas Anlauf brauchen um sich zu verbreiten. +++

Sharing on behalf of BetweenGigs Casting!!

New Hampshire Casting Call for Non-Union Actors!!

Local Casting for a Sci-Fi trailer.

Casting two actors for a proof-of-concept trailer for an episodic sci-fi thriller. It will be shot at the state of the art Studio Lab facility in Derry NH in mid January. This is a paid gig. Both union and non union talent may submit. A Travel/Lodging budget is available, should talent cast be from outside the New England market.

Please see the details below and submit your materials to casting@humanoriginals.com by end of day Sunday, November 23. Please include contact information for your agent or manager if you have one.

************
Project Title: Resonance: Earth 101
Project Type: Proof-of-Concept Trailer
Union: SAG-AFTRA (Micro-Budget Agreement Pending): Roles are open to both union & non union actors.
Production Company: HumanOriginals
Usage: Online, and client/investor/distributer presentations

Shoot Dates: Two days. Tentatively scheduled for January 13 & 14 2026

Shoot Location: Studio Lab, Derry NH

Fit Date/Table Read: TBD. A stipend will be available
Tech Rehearsal Dates (1-2): TBD. A stipend will be available
Travel Stipend/Lodging: TBD, depending on talent's travel distance.

Shoot/Usage Compensation: $1,000/day per talent.
Meals, credit, and copy will also be provided.

SYNOPSIS
Resonance: Earth 101 is a sci-fi thriller proof-of-concept trailer.

Shortly after crashing on Earth in 1983, Kara discovers a mysterious VHS tape in an abandoned warehouse. This triggers a recorded message from Josh, a Brooklyn teen who seems to know her story, even before they’ve met. Through his nervous humor, warnings about Earth, and a mixtape he calls “Earth 101", Josh offers Kara both survival tools and an unexpected connection.

ROLES
JOSH
• Male, 18–25, Black or Mixed Ethnicity
• A hidden tech prodigy from 1983 Brooklyn — sharp, curious, and socially awkward, hiding brilliance behind sarcasm. Nervous yet magnetic. He risks everything to help Kara find her way on Earth.

KARA
• Female, 18–25, Black or Mixed Ethnicity
• A resilient and observant young woman carrying a maturity beyond her years. Athletic and graceful, Kara looks both innocent and ancient, as though she’s already written into myth. Her arrival on Earth sets off an unexpected chain of events.

SUBMISSION INSTRUCTIONS
To be considered for an audition, please email headshot (or current photo), resume, and reel (if available) to casting@humanoriginals.com.

Subject Line of your email should read: Role name / Your name

Submissions are requested by 5:00pm Sunday, November 23. 

If selected to audition, instructions & script for a self-taped audition will be sent to you.

Callbacks, if needed, will be via Zoom.

items.summary:
New Hampshire Casting Call for Non-Union Actors!!

Local Casting for a Sci-Fi trailer.

Casting two actors for a proof-of-concept trailer for an episodic sci-fi thriller. It will be shot at the state of the art Studio Lab facility in Derry NH in mid January. This is a paid gig. Both union and non union talent may submit. A Travel/Lodging budget is available, should talent cast be from outside the New England market.

Please see the details below and submit your materials to casting@humanoriginals.com by end of day Sunday, November 23. Please include contact information for your agent or manager if you have one.

************
Project Title: Resonance: Earth 101
Project Type: Proof-of-Concept Trailer
Union: SAG-AFTRA (Micro-Budget Agreement Pending): Roles are open to both union & non union actors.
Production Company: HumanOriginals
Usage: Online, and client/investor/distributer presentations
Shoot Dates: Two days. Tentatively scheduled for January 13 & 14 2026
Shoot Location: Studio Lab, Derry NH (https://studiolab.one/)
Fit Date/Table Read: TBD. A stipend will be available
Tech Rehearsal Dates (1-2): TBD. A stipend will be available
Travel Stipend/Lodging: TBD, depending on talent's travel distance.

Shoot/Usage Compensation: $1,000/day per talent.
Meals, credit, and copy will also be provided.

SYNOPSIS
Resonance: Earth 101 is a sci-fi thriller proof-of-concept trailer.

Shortly after crashing on Earth in 1983, Kara discovers a mysterious VHS tape in an abandoned warehouse. This triggers a recorded message from Josh, a Brooklyn teen who seems to know her story, even before they’ve met. Through his nervous humor, warnings about Earth, and a mixtape he calls “Earth 101", Josh offers Kara both survival tools and an unexpected connection.

ROLES
JOSH
• Male, 18–25, Black or Mixed Ethnicity
• A hidden tech prodigy from 1983 Brooklyn — sharp, curious, and socially awkward, hiding brilliance behind sarcasm. Nervous yet magnetic. He risks everything to help Kara find her way on Earth.

KARA
• Female, 18–25, Black or Mixed Ethnicity
• A resilient and observant young woman carrying a maturity beyond her years. Athletic and graceful, Kara looks both innocent and ancient, as though she’s already written into myth. Her arrival on Earth sets off an unexpected chain of events.

SUBMISSION INSTRUCTIONS
To be considered for an audition, please email headshot (or current photo), resume, and reel (if available) to casting@humanoriginals.com.

Subject Line of your email should read: Role name / Your name

Submissions are requested by 5:00pm Sunday, November 23. 

If selected to audition, instructions & script for a self-taped audition will be sent to you.

Callbacks, if needed, will be via Zoom.

It’s a wrap! Six Commercials with 50 Actors from MA to TX to RI and back to RI for 3 more this week!!  4 Picture cars in TX - RI!! Locations in RI!  

On Set Wrangler, Child Welfare Worker and Production Assistant!  

Catering and Crafty for 4 days! 

I have a new business: ACTORDASH - I don’t just cast ‘em! I deliver them to set!

I jumped in feet first starting in August 2025, and although we still have some administrative work to do; we are officially wrapped!

I am now on Holiday Break and will be gearing up for more filming in January 2026!

During this break I will be doing a massive Talent Scout starting in Rhode Island!

I know I can easily find everyone I need for our Massachusetts needs with a simple post! But, I’ve found it harder to find Actors in Rhode Island.

items.text:
Immersive Theatre Residency

Learn how to work in the space between you and the other.

11 and 12 December
10.00 to 17.00
Theatre Deli 

Join a two day residency exploring the creation of raw and atmospheric immersive performance. Inspired by the research behind Rotten Meat The Old Kip on Meatham Estate, this residency invites participants to work closely with space, character, and narrative to build intense and emotionally charged encounters.
Through task based improvisation and sensory exploration, you will investigate how bodies respond to environments shaped by tension, uncertainty, and resilience. The work will focus on presence, proximity to the audience, and the construction of meaningful and transformative experiences.
Drawing from Vinicius Salles’s fifteen years with Punchdrunk and his own extensive research in immersive theatre, the residency offers a practical insight into how narrative, space, and the audience can function together as active partners in performance.
This residency is suitable for performers, dancers, actors, and artists who are curious about immersive theatre and interested in expanding their creative approach.
Expect a challenging and engaging process that invites vulnerability, reflection, and bold artistic experimentation.
This is for artists who want to shape the unknown.

Secure one of the 10 space available, Claim your space in here: https://buytickets.at/murmurcreations/1954127

Hi!

I am an acting teacher living between NYC and Paris and I am so excited to be launching my new acting program in Paris! I have been an acting teacher at the Yale School of Drama for over 13 years & I have brought together some of the most outstanding teachers for our first summer - and there are more to come!

Please spread the word?! 

So many opportunities to train in play, clown, voice and movement, and physical acting this Winter and Spring in NYC & Paris! ||

Description: Male, White, playing age 25 - 35, Athletic, 5'10+, 80 kg+, with experience playing strong character roles on stage or screen.

£300 for 1-Day-Shoot plus half a day of rehearsals.

Please send in a cover letter with your resume with headshot and your showreel to Davina Brown at k2filmworks@gmail.com Please do not respond in the comments or via DM.

items.text:
Looking for a Father Christmas
 
We’re on the lookout for someone fun and friendly to help spread some holiday cheer!
If you’re an actor between jobs, or a dad/grandad, this could be a perfect little festive gig.
A small immersive Christmas experience to meet Santa, led by our performer elves 🙂
 
Locations:
• Jesse’s House  Parsons Green
• Jaego’s House  Kensal Rise
 
What we provide:
• A Santa costume (or bring your own if you prefer!)
• Use of members-only facilities for your family
• A fun and festive place to spend the lead-up to Christmas
 
Hours: 9:30 AM – 6:00 PM
Dates: 13th, 14th & 18th
Rates: To be discussed
Must have a DBS or be willing to get one
 
Please email kimberley@jaegoshouse.co.uk to express your interest.
Please reach out if you know someone, or comment any Santa Claus companies  it would be much appreciated 🙂
 
Kimberley
xx

**Jigsaw Casting is seeking a Weather Reporter for a Quick Serve Restaurant Campaign across Canada**

We are also open to a host or news reporter. They’re likeable, relatable, charming, and capable of giving an authentic performance. The ideal candidate has real-life reporting experience. The age range is 40s. Someone that knows the weather like the back of their hand, the subtlety and nuances. They’re confident and engaging, with a comedic sensibility.

This will be filming in Toronto. If someone lives far from this area, travel and accommodation will be provided.

**IF YOU KNOW OF SOMEONE, PLEASE PASS THIS ON!**

This is a non union job. Compensation if selected: $3,075.00. Buyout is based on survival of the edit and includes all lifts, edits, versions.

Must be available for these Important dates:

Recall: Wed Nov 26th, 2025 in Toronto Studio or via zoom if you live far away from Toronto.

Wardrobe: Dec 5th, 2025.

Shoot Date: Dec 9th with a weather hold of Dec 10th, 2025.

*Talent will be shooting outside, in Toronto.

Hello! Would you like to be an extra on a student film project? This is your opportunity!

I'm looking for actors for my SFU 4th year Capstone film "Coiled Like the Wolf."

This will be a two-day shoot from **November 21 - November 22. Come either or both days!**

Monetary compensation will not be provided, but you will get free food!

Feel free to bring your friends! The more the merrier!

Email me at **mimnom@icloud.com **if you're interested!

SPEND A FEW HOURS HANGING OUT AND BEING AN EXTRA ON A STUDENT FILM SET! UNPAID SNACKS WILL BE SERVED EMAIL MIMNOM@ICLOUD.COM IF YOU'RE INTERESTED!'

**Szukam modelki na zasadzie TFP  Gliwice/Katowice ( Śląsk )  **

 

   Szukam pań które nie krępują się własnego ciała i chciałaby mieć ciekawą pamiątkę w postaci klimatycznych zdjęć.  Wiem jak bardzo jest ważna akceptacja własnego ciała bo przez to też możemy inaczej funkcjonować. Przez takie zdjęcia można również tego dokonać. Sesja w głównej mierze jest jako taki motywator.

 

Poszukuje kobiety w **wieku od 30 **lat nie koniecznie z doświadczeniem pozowania,  na zasadach Tfp mieszkającej w Gliwicach lub okolicach Zabrze czy Katowice najdalej. Posiadam na wyposażeniu mini studio z kilkoma tłami oraz lampami. Mam również duży wybór kostiumów i gadżetów do wykorzystywania. Główny motyw do kobieta: Piękna i drapieżna! Sama sesja trwa przeważnie od 1,5h do 2h w zalezności od motywów.

** **

**Temat 1 – ‘’Kobieta mafii 1930’’**

Postać kobiety osadzona w 1930 roku w roli bogatej kobiety, która trudni się gangsterstwem. Przewidziane są ujęcia m.in. przy stoliku na którym są pieniądze, wino, rewolwer. Tło jest wydrukowane w formie muru, cegieł. Motyw sensualny.

 

**Temat 2 – ‘’Wampirzyca w baroku 1700’’**

Postać kobiety ubrana najpierw w suknie czarną oraz peleryne z kapturem. Do tego czarna długa peruka oraz czarne paznokcie. W kolejnym etapie sesji motyw sensualny.

 

**Temat 3 – ‘’Duchy lasu’’**

Postać kobiety ubrana w wianek i w pelerynę z otwartym przodem. W dłoni ma zakrwawiony sierp. Usta czarne oraz paznokcie.

 

https://www.maxmodels.pl/lukus_wielki2

**Zapraszam na stronę Facebook Łukasz Magiera – Fotografia**

 

Więcej informacji na Priv

Hej 

Zaczynamy casting do cool projektu znanej marki odzieży sportowej, niestety mamy bardzo mały budżet, ale projekt będzie bardzo fajny + super rezyser, bedzie się czym chwalić na pewno. Bardzo prosimy o pomoc mimo stawek, projekt będzie naprawdę super.

**BARDZO ZAPRASZAMY OSOBY Z TÓJMIASTA BO SHOOT MA TAM MIEJSCE. **

**SZUKAMY:**

1. Chłopaki na hulajnodze  16 - 25  trzech chłopaków, muszą umieć się przemieszczać na hulajnodze, nie mają mieć levelu pro, ciekawa uroda i skille aktorskie. Chłopaki mówią kwestie - bardzo krótkie zdania, proszę się w ogóle tym nie stresować bo to są rzeczy w stylu mhm, okej więc osoba każdej narodowości sobie poradzi  :)

2. Dziewczyna 16 - 25

3. Starsza pani wiek niesprecyzowany, babcia, ale myślę że 65+, siwa.

**TERMINY: **

20.11 - termin zgłoszeń do godziny 18:00 

-**CALLBACK: TBC**

-**PRZYMIARKI: 25.11**

**-TRAVEL DAY: 25.11**

- **ZDJĘCIA 26.11**

**- POWRÓT 27.11**

**PRAWA I STAWKI: **

Co: hero video (do 45'' + 2 x skróty 6'' i 12'') 

Format: 9x16, 4:5 (16:9 tbc)

Co: Sesja produktowa w stylu edytorial 15 zdjęć + some content z sesji (np. kręcony dronem - 2 viedo do 12 sec) 

Prawa: 12 m-c, PL, digital, some (w tym konta klienta i zawodników), PR, prasa, POS klient partnerzy ), events 

2500 zł per bohater z prawami. 

STAWKA ZAWIERA PROWIZJĘ

**ZGŁOSZENIA PROSZĘ WYSYŁAĆ NA E MAILA **

**Slavic.squad.cast@gmail.com **

**W treści e maila proszę wpisać **
1. **Imię i nazwisko **
2. **Wiek **
3. **Do której roli się zgłaszasz **
4. **W jakim mieście mieszkasz **
5. **Numer telefonu **

6. **Czy umiesz jeździć  na hulajnodze **

sharedPost.text:
📣TURNIEJ TAŃCA w Rzeszowie!

🔥INTERNATIONAL DANCE CUP RZESZÓW 2025🔥
Pierwsza edycja. Pierwsza szansa. Pierwszy krok na scenę, która czeka właśnie na Ciebie.
Jeśli taniec to Twój żywioł — to MUSISZ być.🫵🤩
______________________
👉 SOLIŚCI & DUETY 👈

🗓️ Turniej 30.11.2025 r. - niedziela
📍 ul. Moniuszki 2 (I piętro), Centrum Rzeszowa

📩 Zgłoszenia do 23.11.2025 r.❗️
👇Link do formularza zgłoszeniowego wraz z regulaminem
https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfcREPk5clGRe8_O-5lY7o-zc0YlR0Ti8_Dm4OQ2xXDWUPdXg/viewform?usp=header

📲 Nie czekaj, zgłoś się już dziś!😉 
💃TAŃCZ, TAŃCZ, TAŃCZ🕺

_________________________________
✨Kategorie taneczne & wiekowe:✨

1️⃣ Modern/ Contemporary/ Jazz/ Jazz Funk 💫
~ 10-13 lat
~ 14-17
~ 18+
-> Duety: od 10 roku życia

2️⃣ Commercial/ Hip Hop 👟
~ 10-13 lat
~ 14-17
~ 18+
-> Duety: od 10 roku życia

3️⃣ High Heels/ Latino Solo 👠
~ 16+
-> Duety: 16+
__________________

🎟️ Opłata wpisowa: 50 zł za osobę za jedną kategorię

⏳Czas prezentacji:
- Soliści: 1:30 min
- Duety: 2 min 

__________________
🔥Dlaczego warto?

→ Bo to turniej stworzony z prawdziwej pasji. Atmosfera będzie ciepła, motywująca i pełna dobrej energii.

→ Scena daje impuls. Każdy występ rozwija — a ten może dodać Ci skrzydeł.

→ Bo to idealna okazja, żeby zrobić coś dla siebie: sprawdzić się, poczuć ten moment na scenie i dać przestrzeń swojej tanecznej stronie.

→ Poznajesz nowych tancerzy i ludzi z podobnym flow, vibe-em😉 To naturalnie otwiera głowę, poszerza perspektywę i daje kontakt z osobami, które pasjonują się tym samym co Ty.

→ Łapiesz doświadczenie turniejowe bez presji przeogromnej sceny. Adrenalina, emocje, rywalizacja — ale w atmosferze, w której da się oddychać.

→ Pierwsza edycja ma swój klimat. Tego nie da się powtórzyć — jesteś częścią nowej historii🥰

__________________________________
Więcej informacji:
→ ☎️ +48 780 500 410
→ 💌 wiadomości DM
__________________________________
